<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="assets/css/plugins/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- fonts and icons -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href='https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.1/css/boxicons.min.css' rel='stylesheet'>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.8.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <!-- aos  -->
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/responsive.css">
    <title>Home | Sankar Media</title>
    <title>About Us | Sankar Media</title>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- navbar  -->
  {{>Navbar}}

    <!-- main header  -->
    <section class="container-fluid main_header mt-3">

        <div class="row ">
            <div class="col-md-10 col-12 mx-auto ">
                <div class="row main_hero">
                    <!-- main hero left  -->
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-6 hero_left">
                        <p class="up_heading">Creative solutions to digital challenges</p>
                        <h1 class="main_heading">Innnovate Solution for </h1>
                        <p class="main_heading autoType">Digital Marketing</p>
                        <p class="main_para">Let's Generate some Leads !</p>

                        <a href="#" class="btn main_btn me-3">Contact Us</a>

                    </div>

                    <!-- main header right  -->
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-6 hero_right ">
                        <img src="assets/img/about-us.webp" alt="" class="main_hero_img about_hero_img">
                       </div>

                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        

    </section>

    <!-- About section  -->
    <section class="container-fluid  my-5">


        <!-- why choose us  -->
        <div class="container" data-aos="fade-right">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-9">
                    <h2 class="heading heading-left mb-3">About Us</h2>
                    
                    <p class="text-light para para-left mt-5">SankarMedia happens to be one of the pioneering, creative, & most importantly client-friendly digital marketing service providers in the market. We work towards the satisfaction of our clients and deliver the highest quality standards.</p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container" style="margin-top: 5rem;">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 Aboutimg">
                    <img src="assets/img/home/2.png" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="fade-left">
                    <h2 class="heading heading-right mb-3">Who us</h2>
                    <p class="text-light para mt-5">SankarMedia is one of the market's most innovative, creative, and, most importantly, client-friendly digital marketing service providers. We work hard to ensure that our clients are satisfied and that we meet the highest quality requirements.</p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <!-- counter  -->
        <div class="container mt-3">
            <div class="row">

                <div class="col-md-3 col-6 p-3 Count_Box">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center ">
                        <p class="countNum">500</p>
                        <div class="ms-3">
                            <i class='bx bxs-certification countIcon'></i>
                            <p class="countTitle text-light">Experience</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                
                <div class="col-md-3 col-6 p-3 Count_Box">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <p class="countNum">700</p>
                        <div class="ms-3">
                            <i class='bx bxs-bookmarks countIcon'></i>
                            <p class="countTitle text-light">Total Project</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-3 col-6 p-3 Count_Box">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <p class="countNum">400</p>
                        <div class="ms-3">
                            <i class='bx bxs-smile countIcon'></i>
                            <p class="countTitle text-light">Happy Clients</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-3 col-6 p-3 Count_Box">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <p class="countNum">200</p>
                        <div class="ms-3">
                            <i class='bx bxs-trophy countIcon'></i>
                            <p class="countTitle text-light">Achivements</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>


            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="container" style="margin-top: 5rem;">
            <h2 class="heading mb-3 mx-auto">OUR STORY</h2>
            <p class="text-light para text-center mt-3" style="width: 80%; margin: auto;">At Sankar Media, our prime objective is to place our clients' brand image high on the growth curve, generate leads and drive sales. We channel every possible effort in providing them a competitive edge over their contemporaries in the market. Sankar Media is also a pioneer in Content Creation, Animation, Video Editing, Graphic designing, SEO & Email & Mobile marketing, and many more. We are strengthening our knowledge base and continually researching for brand new Conceptual Marketing, Link-building, and Backlink strategies for our esteemed clientele. SankarMedia takes pride in its strong portfolio of highly gratified clientele, thus continually driving innovation across industry verticals.</p>

            <p class="text-light para text-center mt-3" style="width: 90%; margin: auto;">Our primary goal at Sankar Media is to raise the profile of our clients' brands, create leads, and increase sales. We focus all of our efforts on giving them a competitive advantage over their market competitors. Sankar Media is a leader in a variety of fields, including content creation, animation, video editing, graphic design, SEO, email, and mobile marketing, among others. For our prestigious clients, we are constantly expanding our knowledge base and seeking for brand new Conceptual Marketing, Link-building, and Backlink tactics. SankarMedia is proud of its long list of satisfied clients, which keeps the company at the forefront of industry innovation.</p>
            
        </div>






    </section>
     <!-- newsletter  -->
    {{>Newsletter}}
    <!-- footer band  -->
    {{>FooterBand}}
    <!-- footer  -->
    {{>Footer}}

